comments.comment:
Part god, part man, the king that ruled over the city-state of Uruk in Sumeria before the modern calendar.
A king not just of legend but of one of mankind's oldest tales, "The Epic of Gilgamesh."

Height/Weight: 182cm, 68kg
Origin: Sumerian Civilization, The Epic of Gilgamesh
Region: Babylonia, Uruk
Alignment: Chaotic-Good
Gender: Male

Ruthless and merciless, he does not listen to others.
He's a tyrant who sees his standards as absolute.
This Heroic Spirit clearly overpowers all the others, and unleashes his overwhelming wealth like water.

Divinity: B (A+)
He has the highest affinity with divine spirits, but because he hates the gods it has been ranked down.
A demi-god with 2/3 divinity and 1/3 humanity, he is matchless in his reign over the world.
He is a supreme being who has obtained everything in existence.

『Gate of Babylon』
Rank: E~A++
NP Type: Anti-Personnel 
Treasury of the King.
A key-shaped sword that connects to the Golden Capital.
It bridges different spaces, and allows the user to freely take any treasure from the vault.
The more riches the user accrues, the more powerful the attack.
It's used as a normal attack in this game.

『Enuma Elish』
Rank: EX
NP Type: Anti-World
Star of Creation that Divided Heaven and Earth.
Crowned with the name of a Mesopotamian god, the sword Ea can cause a rupture in space.
One of the most powerful Noble Phantasms, it is a sword that can "cut apart worlds."

Gilgamesh is a treasure collector.
He often says "I've already collected all the wealth in this world."
That is not an overstatement.
He has gathered, stored, and sealed away every prototype of every technology known to man.
In his own words, "humans are foolish, but the items, and civilizations humans create are of value."

voiceLines.name: Birthday
voiceLines.subtitle: Your birthday? Should I care?

voiceLines.name: During an Event
voiceLines.subtitle: The festivities have started again. You may go, Mongrel.

voiceLines.name: Conversation 1
voiceLines.subtitle: Make your preparations! I can't stand this boredom!

voiceLines.name: Conversation 2
voiceLines.subtitle: Be sure you don't bore me, Mongrel.

voiceLines.name: Conversation 3
voiceLines.subtitle:
Our Servant-Master relationship?
Don't be so bold as to think I serve you. You merely rally me to action.

voiceLines.name: Likes
voiceLines.subtitle:
The treasures of this world are mine to be had.
No matter what they may be, all of it is mine for the taking.

voiceLines.name: Dislikes
voiceLines.subtitle: Dislikes? Those who don't push themselves to the limit are boring. That is the difference between a man and a beast.

voiceLines.name: About the Holy Grail
voiceLines.subtitle:
The Holy Grail? It would make for the perfect wine glass.
If not for its bloody taste.

voiceLines.name: Bond Level 1
voiceLines.subtitle:
This battle is nothing to me but a pastime.
There's nothing that merits my true effort, after all.

voiceLines.name: Bond Level 2
voiceLines.subtitle:
Is there any end to my treasures?
Why yes, of course.
But that sits right at the very limit of human knowledge. Well, one day you'll understand.

voiceLines.name: Bond Level 3
voiceLines.subtitle:
It seems you have worked with other Heroic Spirits.
It can't be helped for a mere commoner like you. 
But I am disappointed. At least pick someone worthy to stand next to me.

voiceLines.name: Bond Level 4
voiceLines.subtitle:
What? I'm not as strong as I say? Careless, even?
Nonsense. What is a king without an ego! Now then, stand proud!

voiceLines.name: Bond Level 5
voiceLines.subtitle:
Simple as you are, you fight well, Mongrel.
Yes, most intriguing. Perhaps you are worthy of my real power after all...

voiceLines.name: Birthday
voiceLines.subtitle: Your birthday is it? Fool, you should grant me at least a week's notice!

voiceLines.name: Level up
voiceLines.subtitle: Bwahaha!

voiceLines.name: Ascension 2
voiceLines.subtitle: [id 200200_0_G020]Calm yourself, this is nothing.

voiceLines.name: Ascension 1
voiceLines.subtitle: [id 200200_0_G030]It's still a long way to reclaim my original form. Keep up your work.

voiceLines.name: Ascension 3
voiceLines.subtitle: [id 200200_0_G040]We are almost there. Don't mess it up now, Mongrel.

voiceLines.name: Ascension 4
voiceLines.subtitle: [id 200200_0_G050]Hmph, well done for a mere man. [delay 4.2]Allow me to reward your determination with mankind's most ancient treasure. [id 200200_0_G051]Of course, this is for you and you alone.

voiceLines.name: Summon
text: Hahaha! For you to summon me like this, I see your luck has run out, Mongrel!
voiceLines.subtitle: Hahaha! For you to summon me like this, I see your luck has run out, Mongrel!

voiceLines.name: Attack 1
voiceLines.subtitle: Hmph!

voiceLines.name: Attack 2
voiceLines.subtitle: Hyah!

voiceLines.name: Attack 3
voiceLines.subtitle: Bwahahaha!

voiceLines.name: Extra Attack
voiceLines.subtitle: Don't get cocky!

voiceLines.name: Skill 1
voiceLines.subtitle: Let me raise my focus.

voiceLines.name: Skill 2
voiceLines.subtitle: Struggle all you desire!

voiceLines.name: Battle Start 1
voiceLines.subtitle: For a Mongrel, you sure know how to bark.

voiceLines.name: Battle Start 2
voiceLines.subtitle: Get lost, you insolent fool.

voiceLines.name: Victory 1
voiceLines.subtitle: What is a king without an ego?

voiceLines.name: Victory 2
voiceLines.subtitle: This is what you call domination!

voiceLines.name: Damage 2
voiceLines.subtitle: Nghh!

voiceLines.name: Damage 1
voiceLines.subtitle: Why you! You! YOU!

voiceLines.name: Incapacitated 1
voiceLines.subtitle: Losing to a Mongrel like you!

voiceLines.name: Incapacitated 2
voiceLines.subtitle: Very well, I'll retreat this time!

voiceLines.name: Command Card 1
voiceLines.subtitle: Hmph!

voiceLines.name: Command Card 2
voiceLines.subtitle: Boring.

voiceLines.name: Command Card 3
voiceLines.subtitle: How curious.

voiceLines.name: Noble Phantasm Card
voiceLines.subtitle: I shall unlock my vault.

voiceLines.name: Noble Phantasm
voiceLines.subtitle:
[id 200200_0_B050]Judgment is upon you. Behold the crushing might of my Sword of Rupture
[id 200200_0_B052]—Behold
[id 200200_0_B053]Enuma Elish!
